<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,284,419]" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">
Recently, 
<bibRefCitation author="Botero, J. &amp; Santos-Silva, A. &amp; Bezark, L. G." box="[265,491,284,311]" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" pagination="69 - 100" refId="ref12060" refString="Botero, J. P, Santos-Silva, A. &amp; Bezark, L. G. (2019) Revision of the genus Pteroplatus Buquet, 1840 (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Cerambycinae) and taxonomic notes in Pteroplatini. Zootaxa, 4658 (1), 69 - 100. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4658.1.3" type="journal article" year="2019">
Botero 
<emphasis box="[349,407,284,310]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">et al.</emphasis>
(2019)
</bibRefCitation>
revised the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Buquet, 1840" authorityName="Buquet" authorityYear="1840" box="[706,999,284,311]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Pteroplatus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[706,836,284,310]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">Pteroplatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Buquet, J. B. L." box="[844,999,285,311]" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" pagination="287" refId="ref12262" refString="Buquet, J. B. L. (1840) Une notice sur un genre nouveau de longicornes, de la tribu des cerambycins, et designe sous le nom de Pteroplatus, dans la troisieme edition du catalogue de M. le Comte Dejean. Revue Zoologique, 1840, 287." type="journal article" year="1840">Buquet, 1840</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and listed new junior synonyms of 
<taxonomicName authority="Buquet, 1840" authorityName="Buquet" authorityYear="1840" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Pteroplatus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulcher">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">P. pulcher</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Buquet, J. B. L." box="[244,399,321,347]" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" pagination="287" refId="ref12262" refString="Buquet, J. B. L. (1840) Une notice sur un genre nouveau de longicornes, de la tribu des cerambycins, et designe sous le nom de Pteroplatus, dans la troisieme edition du catalogue de M. le Comte Dejean. Revue Zoologique, 1840, 287." type="journal article" year="1840">Buquet, 1840</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. However, they forget to include 
<taxonomicName authority="Buquet, 1840" authorityName="Buquet" authorityYear="1840" box="[776,1061,320,347]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Pteroplatus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="suturalis">
<emphasis box="[776,902,320,346]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">P. suturalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Buquet, J. B. L." box="[910,1061,321,347]" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" pagination="287" refId="ref12262" refString="Buquet, J. B. L. (1840) Une notice sur un genre nouveau de longicornes, de la tribu des cerambycins, et designe sous le nom de Pteroplatus, dans la troisieme edition du catalogue de M. le Comte Dejean. Revue Zoologique, 1840, 287." type="journal article" year="1840">Buquet, 1840</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
as a new synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Buquet" authorityYear="1840" box="[1316,1430,320,346]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Pteroplatus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="167" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulcher">
<emphasis box="[1316,1430,320,346]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">P. pulcher</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Examination of the photograph of the 
<typeStatus box="[573,671,356,382]" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">holotype</typeStatus>
(
<figureCitation box="[686,766,356,383]" captionStart="FIGURES 16–17" captionStartId="10.[151,264,1084,1109]" captionTargetBox="[184,1404,450,1043]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[151,1435,440,1058]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 16–17. Pteroplatus suturalis, holotype: 16) Dorsal habitus; 17) Labels." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3730909" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3730909/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="167">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
) sent by Gérard L. Tavakilian (MNHN), as well as the original description, provide evidence for the synonymy.
</paragraph>
